    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Alabaster Module</title>

      <para>
        The <application>Alabaster</application> package is a theme for the
<application>sphinx</application> documentation system. Although developed
separately, it is the default theme for sphinx.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

